ice相关延迟\n\n### 4. **影响范围**\n- 主要影响购物车操作(EmptyCart, GetCart)和结账流程\n- 异常持续时间约14分钟，符合用户查询的时间范围\n- 涉及多个节点(aiops-k8s-01,03,04,05,07,08)，表明是分布式系统问题\n\n**结论**: Redis数据库性能问题是本次异常的根本原因，导致整个购物车和结账系统出现严重延迟。\n\n--- Previous Consensus Decision ---\nNo consensus yet", "metric_analysis_findings": "See Log Findings for Full Context", "trace_analysis_findings": "See Log Findings for Full Context", "consensus_decision": "AGREED", "current_hypothesis": "redis-cart-0 is the root cause due to severe Redis database performance degradation"}
